{"id":618490,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/09/原姗姗：我愿意是人质/","date":"2019-09-26T03:44:17Z","modified":"2019-09-26T03:57:58Z","title":"原姗姗：我愿意是人质","content":"<p>CDT编者按：被大陆关押的台湾人李明哲的父亲近日去世，其妻子李净瑜希望监狱中的丈夫可以回家奔丧，自己愿意做人质。709律师家属原姗姗发文，表示也愿意为人质，让李明哲可以回家奔丧。</p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-618491 aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/image_from_ios.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1619\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/image_from_ios.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/image_from_ios-93x300.jpg 93w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/image_from_ios-768x2486.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/09/image_from_ios-316x1024.jpg 316w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案| <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%93%B2\">李明哲</a></strong></p>\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-568105 size-thumbnail aligncenter\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/a33df76a71374ec6a8ae344396301667-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/a33df76a71374ec6a8ae344396301667-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/09/a33df76a71374ec6a8ae344396301667-70x70.jpg 70w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></p>\n","author":251,"categories":[18271,38912,9203],"tags":[38964,32619]}